  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Toast the bread slices in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "In a blender, combine coconut milk, cashew nuts, nam prik pao, fish sauce, and lime juice, and blend until smooth.",
    "In a paella pan, combine the blended mixture and toasted bread slices.",
    "Top the bread slices with a scoop of coconut ice cream.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds and salt over the ice cream.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional toasted cashew nuts if desired."
